{"tid":1430611,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"求解夢 發夢夢見自己撞邪","createTime":"2019-08-07T19:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T02:22:34.000Z","uid":186668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a0c1e8ea0094dc57fdf538472c94221a930a24e5","tid":1430611,"uid":186668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:19:11.000Z","msg":"個夢夢境<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n前段好零碎唔記得自己做過d 咩<br />\n後段夢到自己訓教唔知點解床到有枝針<br />\n我吉中左左手 因為我係發緊夢 我係濛糊中夾硬抆佢出黎<br />\n抆都唔易 佢吉到好入 皮膚收縮 好難先夾硬抆佢出黎<br />\n一訓醒頭昏腦漲 左手亦有兩個血洞<br />\n訓醒入廁所照鏡見到自己個樣面色蒼白 好邪惡好心寒<br />\n雙眼仲識發藍光 總知睇落好恐怖 嚇到我唔敢再照鏡<br />\n我問屋企人 我係咪睇落同平時唔同樣 佢話係<br />\n跟住反應就係知道自己咁樣一定返唔到學叫我屋企人幫我請病假<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n然後到咁上下我就醒左, 訓醒冇出冷汗<br />\n<br />\nPS 好耐冇發過惡夢, 唔知關唔關臨訓前睇完幾集砍殺類美劇事<br />\nPPS 我用開右手, 不過左手慣常亦都有d 特定用途<br />\nPPPS 個夢俾我感覺係睇返自己陰暗面, 越諗越恐怖, 呢期7月有d 心寒想上黎問下"},{"pid":"fa9f0f60e9f123ef95baabe696ae81fa38191532","tid":1430611,"uid":143435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:22:36.000Z","msg":"轉睇咸片，再用左手打打丁，定一定驚就冇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986b19a147b8442dd27d58af1c8867efb3e9bc70","tid":1430611,"uid":186668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa9f0f60e9f123ef95baabe696ae81fa38191532","tid":1430611,"uid":143435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:22:36.000Z","msg":"轉睇咸片，再用左手打打丁，定一定驚就冇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e2126a16909ae0bbdd628aaa4966121acf6baf","tid":1430611,"uid":143435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"986b19a147b8442dd27d58af1c8867efb3e9bc70","tid":1430611,"uid":186668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa9f0f60e9f123ef95baabe696ae81fa38191532","tid":1430611,"uid":143435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:22:36.000Z","msg":"轉睇咸片，再用左手打打丁，定一定驚就冇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:35:30.000Z","msg":"咁下世見啦，有咩想交低<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7ada9e8e91e4daf1aa2dbf6d5ff5f6f28d6566","tid":1430611,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:47:39.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"a37a58471db30a2a56c968882b5ad37f45b02d57","tid":1430611,"uid":186668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a7ada9e8e91e4daf1aa2dbf6d5ff5f6f28d6566","tid":1430611,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:47:39.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:00:25.000Z","msg":"天地有正氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n面對黑警 無需害怕"},{"pid":"2497c96f5aa4990b63a56fc85fcf65613bf2ff7e","tid":1430611,"uid":186668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6229f004feaaebeec4a2d2f62021988481da6c81","tid":1430611,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:22:34.000Z","msg":"奇怪嘢一次半次不能作準"}]}